Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ok 很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快连上转播
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们赶去现场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 奇莎 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 手忙脚乱地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 这又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在等这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.25,0:20:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 看穿了不能发射镭射的时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅速充电
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
