Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.17,0:20:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:20:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了
