Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.78,0:21:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是美利坚合众国总统的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.83,0:21:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 立刻停止战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修兹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 来迟了 乔伊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米纳米博士 立即投降
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗到此已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修兹
